            <title>[NET-268] SubnetUtilsTest  does not include any tests for CIDR with /30, /31, /32</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NET-268</link>
                <project id="12310487" key="NET">Commons Net</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SubnetUtilsTest  does not include any tests for CIDRs with masks of /30, /31, /32&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It only includes tests for /8 /16 /24 and /29, plus a test for the (invalid) /0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
